Nagamba ngu : “ Abaana abandukusoma nabo tibatiina kubazaaho ebintu ebi bakora .
Ha kiro eki , obukaikuru n’obukaikuru bw’abantu kuruga omu mahanga maingi , kandi ab’erangi ezirukwahukana boleka nk’oku barukukigumya ngu Yahwe akatuma Omwana we .
Hanyuma y’okubisoma , omu iraka eri lyonyine , yatura ebigambo eby’orukarra rwona otakaikize .
( Yohana 6 : 44 ) Nahabweki aine ensonga habwaki nabagonza .
Abanyanzigwa ba Yesu bakalengaho kumutahya omu nsonga ezirukukwata ha kusasura omusoro .
Guli mulingo gw’amaani ogu tusobora kwolekeramu Yahwe ngu nitumugonza kandi nitumusiima byona ebi atukoliire .
Nirusobora kuba rwali rubuga orw’abantu abayangire kukonyera Baraka omu bulemu .
Soma Okubanza 40 : 14 , 15 .
( Yobu 23 : 12 ) Akagambira Yahwe ati : “ Nkahurra habwokuhurra okwamatu . ”
Eki tikihikire habwokuba nikiba nikihakaniza emiringo ya Ruhanga .
Obwire obumu , Yahwe yafubiraga rundi yabaihaga omu bwebembezi .
Emyaka ikumi eyabandize ey’obulemi bwa Asa , Yuda ekaikara etarumu obulemu .
Ruhanga akagambira Musa ati : “ Manyire obujune bwabu . ”
Bakatamu ekitiinisa abasaija abayebemberaga ekitebe , kandi naitwe eki nikyo tukora omu kasumi kanu .
Kiro kimu , John akatumwa ise nukwo atwale ebbahasa hali ow’oruganda omu kitebe .
Baibuli eyoleka ngu obugumisiriza buletwa omwoyo gwa Ruhanga .
Akacwamu kukora ki ?
Kugonza muno amakuru amarungi nikyo ekyamwekambisize kwikara n’atebeza n’obu baraaba bamuhiganiize muno .
Baitu tusemeriire kwegendereza kurora ensonga enu tiyaturuga omu bitekerezo .
( Okubanza 1 : 28 ) Kakuba Adamu na Hawa bafiire batakazaire abaana , ekigendererwa kya Ruhanga eky’okwijuza ensi n’abaana babo kyakubaire kifiire .
( Matayo 11 : 19 ) Ago tigali mananu ?
Omu 1939 , Obulemi obw’Ensi Yoona Obwakabiri bukatandika .
Batekerezaho muno amasomo agaramusikiriza batakabalize nauwe .
Baitu hati Yesica akaba acwiremu kuheereza Yahwe .
Wekaguze , ‘ Esaara enu nenyegesa ki hali Danieri ? ’
